/p>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">V\u00e4lj wavegardiner f\u00f6r funktionalitet och anpassningsbarhet<\/h3>\n<p>V\u00e5r wavegardin \u00e4r inte bara en estetisk h\u00f6jdpunkt i rummet, utan ocks\u00e5 en symbol f\u00f6r funktionalitet och anpassningsbarhet. Den erbjuder en perfekt balans mellan ljus och privatliv, vilket g\u00f6r den idealisk f\u00f6r alla typer av inomhusmilj\u00f6er, fr\u00e5n kontor till bost\u00e4der.<\/p>\n<p>Med olika typer av tyg och f\u00e4rger att v\u00e4lja mellan, kan wavegardinen anpassas f\u00f6r att m\u00f6ta specifika behov, vare sig om du vill att dina gardiner ska filtrera dagsljuset eller agera rumsavdelare.<\/p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/kostnadsfritt-hembesok-BTN.png&#8221; title_text=&#8221;kostnadsfritt hembeso\u0308k- BTN&#8221; url=&#8221;\/hem\/#hembasok\/&#8221; show_bottom_space=&#8221;off&#8221; align=&#8221;right&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; transform_translate=&#8221;30px|0px&#8221; transform_translate_linked=&#8221;off&#8221; transform_rotate=&#8221;0deg|0deg|10deg&#8221; position_origin_a=&#8221;center_center&#8221; position_origin_r=&#8221;bottom_right&#8221; width=&#8221;150px&#8221; width_tablet=&#8221;150px&#8221; width_phone=&#8221;120px&#8221; width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;40px||||false|false&#8221; animation_style=&#8221;slide&#8221; animation_direction=&#8221;right&#8221; animation_duration=&#8221;1500ms&#8221; animation_intensity_slide=&#8221;30%&#8221; border_radii=&#8221;on|10px|10px|10px|10px&#8221; box_shadow_style=&#8221;preset3&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; transform_styles__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|hover&#8221; transform_scale__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|hover&#8221; transfo